{"tid":2354771,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"★網傳中國國藥疫苗說明書　多達73種副作用  惟有關發文已被刪除","createTime":"2021-01-05T17:08:21.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-08T05:57:06.000Z","uid":19454,"like":34,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":32,"replies":[{"pid":"28e82e91a23f3edb95af21a56acb0770fa5eaf74","tid":2354771,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-01-05T17:08:21.000Z","msg":"中國國藥集團的新冠肺炎滅活疫苗，近日獲批准上市，其保護效力達79%。不少網民日前轉發內地疫苗專家陶黎納在微信的發文，後者附上國藥疫苗的說明書，聲稱是「世界上最不安全的疫苗」，接種後副作用達73種，<span class=\"xx-large\"><strong>惟有關發文事後已被刪除</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n網傳圖片顯示，陶黎納表示收到國藥疫苗最新的電子版說明書，其核准日期為去年12月30日。惟說明書上記載的「不良反應」，共73種局部或全身不良反應，除了接種部位疼痛、頭痛外，當中更包括或會可能出現高血壓、視力減退、喪失味覺及尿失禁等嚴重副作用，罕見副作用則有紅斑、月經延遲等。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/cnnews/20210105/photo/bkn-20210105211403608-0105_00952_001_02b.jpg?20210106001706\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fcnnews%2F20210105%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20210105211403608-0105_00952_001_02b.jpg%3F20210106001706&h=6751ee74&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/cnnews/20210105/bkn-20210105211403608-0105_00952_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fcnnews%2F20210105%2Fbkn-20210105211403608-0105_00952_001.html&d=QL2FFPepynYtbGyOTzoAG1SbKypX9O9wpAPGBeI%2BXHg%3D&h=3a962c8c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/cnnews/20210105/bkn-20210105211403608-0105_00952_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"65c92d0aad3d777da7dacb808fdc4289aecae1bb","tid":2354771,"uid":19454,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2021-01-05T17:08:48.000Z","msg":"惟有關發文事後已被刪除<br />\n惟有關發文事後已被刪除<br />\n惟有關發文事後已被刪除<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gi